node_modules folder
    - contains node packages used in the project

public folder
    - available to the browser
    - pulled to the browser with the id of root

src folder
    - project workspace

package.json
    - configuration for the project

index.js
    - entry point to the application

components folder
    - is where we store are project components

Library | styled-components
    - yarn add styled-components

State in React
    - application will react to changes in the application State
    - state is informtion being stored into a variable that is stored in the react framework
    - state is essentially data
    - state is controlled by invoking react hooks

    

